{"article_id":"KZinToYH2O1LKtOh","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump warned Friday","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"that","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"if Democrats do not agree to his demands","depth":11},{"id":3,"text":"to fund a wall on the southern border ,","depth":11},{"id":4,"text":"he will \" close the Southern border entirely \"","depth":11},{"id":5,"text":"and cut aid to Central American countries","depth":11},{"id":6,"text":"-- while pulling back on trade with Mexico .","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"\" We will be forced to close the Southern Border entirely","depth":11},{"id":8,"text":"if the Obstructionist Democrats do not give us the money","depth":11},{"id":9,"text":"to finish the Wall","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"& also change the ridiculous immigration laws","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"that our Country is saddled with , \"","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"he tweeted Friday morning .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"\" Hard to believe","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"there was a Congress & President","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"who would approve ! \"","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"The tweetstorm came amid the partial government shutdown","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"that will soon enter its second week .","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"The closures began last Saturday","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"after Republicans and Democrats were unable to agree on a funding package","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"that would keep the government open","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"and fund Trump ' s promised border wall .","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"Trump has demanded $ 5 billion for the barrier ,","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"but Democrats have refused ,","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"instead offering $ 1.3 billion for general border security .","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"With both sides refusing to budge and little activity on Capitol Hill amid the holiday break , there are no signs of the impasse ending anytime soon .","depth":5},{"id":26,"text":"One member of the House Republican leadership told on Thursday","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"that a resolution may not emerge until the new year .","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"But on Friday , Trump not only renewed his demands for the wall ,","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"but threatened numerous consequences in the absence of that money .","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"He even suggested","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"pulling back on the recently renegotiated North American Free Trade Agreement","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"( NAFTA ) ,","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"which now goes by the United States-Mexico-Canada Agreement","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"( USMCA ) .","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"\" The United States looses","depth":13},{"id":36,"text":"[ sic ]","depth":13},{"id":37,"text":"soooo much money on Trade with Mexico under NAFTA , over 75 Billion Dollars a year","depth":13},{"id":38,"text":"( not including Drug Money","depth":14},{"id":39,"text":"which would be many times that amount ) ,","depth":14},{"id":40,"text":"that I would consider closing the Southern Border a 'profit making operation , ' ''","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"he tweeted .","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"\" Bring our car industry back into the United States","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"where it belongs .","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"Go back to pre-NAFTA ,","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"before so many of our companies and jobs were so foolishly sent to Mexico , \"","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"he carried on .","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"\" Either we build","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"( finish )","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"the Wall","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"or we close the Border . \"","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"He then said","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"the U.S. would terminate aid with Honduras , Guatemala and El Salvador ,","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"which","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"he said","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"are doing \" nothing for the United States","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"but taking our money , \"","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"and referred to reports","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"that another caravan of migrants","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"hoping to get to the U.S.","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"is planning on leaving Honduras in January .","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"\" Word is that a new Caravan is forming in Honduras","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"and they are doing nothing about it .","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"We will be cutting off all aid to these 3 countries","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"- taking advantage of U.S. for years ! \"","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"Trump has previously threatened to shut down the border ,","depth":4},{"id":67,"text":"but took no action","depth":6},{"id":68,"text":"to do so","depth":6},{"id":69,"text":"following those threats .","depth":5},{"id":70,"text":"He also previously threatened to cut aid to countries","depth":5},{"id":71,"text":"that assist ,","depth":6},{"id":72,"text":"or do nothing","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"to stop , the caravans .","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"But earlier this month , the U.S. pledged a total of $ 10.6 billion in aid and investment for Central America and southern Mexico","depth":5},{"id":75,"text":"-- as part of a push","depth":6},{"id":76,"text":"to promote better security and job opportunities","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"so that Central Americans and Mexicans do not have to emigrate to the U.S .","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"NIELSEN ANNOUNCES DEAL WITH MEXICO","depth":4},{"id":79,"text":"TO OVERHAUL ASYLUM PROCESS ,","depth":5},{"id":80,"text":"COMBAT 'CATCH AND RELEASE '","depth":5},{"id":81,"text":"A cut-off of trade relations with Mexico could also risk a new agreement","depth":5},{"id":82,"text":"that DHS Secretary Kirstjen Nielsen announced this month","depth":5},{"id":83,"text":"that calls for immigrants","depth":6},{"id":84,"text":"claiming asylum in the U.S.","depth":6},{"id":85,"text":"to be returned to Mexico","depth":6},{"id":86,"text":"as their cases are processed .","depth":6},{"id":87,"text":"Mick Mulvaney , Trump ' s incoming acting chief of staff , claimed Friday on \" Fox & Friends \"","depth":6},{"id":88,"text":"that it appeared Senate Democratic Leader Chuck Schumer is interested in a deal","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"but Speaker-designate Nancy Pelosi is preventing it .","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"He alleged","depth":6},{"id":91,"text":"Democrats are not dealing","depth":7},{"id":92,"text":"because Pelosi is waiting","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"until she secures the speakership .","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"\" We don ' t think","depth":6},{"id":95,"text":"they will","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"[ negotiate ]","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"until after the new Congress is sworn in , \"","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"he said .","depth":5},{"id":99,"text":"But Pelosi has denied claims","depth":5},{"id":100,"text":"they have n't provided a counteroffer .","depth":5},{"id":101,"text":"`` Democrats have offered Republicans three options","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"to re-open government","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"that all include funding for strong , sensible , and effective border security","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"- but not the President 's immoral , ineffective and expensive wall , ''","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"said Drew Hammill , Pelosi 's deputy chief of staff .","depth":6},{"id":106,"text":"`` With the House Majority , Democrats will act swiftly","depth":7},{"id":107,"text":"to end the Trump Shutdown ,","depth":7},{"id":108,"text":"and will fight for a strategic , robust national security policy ,","depth":7},{"id":109,"text":"including strong and smart border security , and strong support for our servicemembers and veterans . ''","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":219,"left":187,"right":218,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":187,"left":175,"right":186,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":175,"left":134,"right":174,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"par